797
01:13:48,716 --> 01:13:49,717
¡Déjenme salir!

798
01:13:50,343 --> 01:13:51,344
¡Déjenme salir!

799
01:13:53,679 --> 01:13:56,182
- ¡Por favor, mamá, déjame salir!
- Rose.

800
01:13:56,557 --> 01:13:58,059
¡Déjenme salir!

801
01:13:58,768 --> 01:13:59,768
Rose.

802
